pageContext.claim: “By the way, without the plague from China, this thing was over. This was over. We were sailing. But that came in, and then you have to prove yourself again. So now I have to prove myself again.”
pageContext.analysis: Polling showed Trump was behind Joe Biden even before the coronavirus pandemic emerged. That was a key reason why Trump urged the Ukrainian president to investigate Biden -- because he viewed Biden as his strongest possible opponent.
